    "description": {
      "value": "<em>You have learned to let your armor bear the brunt of the worst attacks.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Proficient with armor or shield.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>If an opponent scores a critical hit against you, you can turn the critical hit into a normal hit. If you do, either your armor or your shield gains the broken condition (your choice).<br/><br/><b>Combat Trick</b><br/>When you use this feat to negate a critical hit, you can spend 5 stamina points to give your armor or shield a 50% chance to avoid gaining the broken condition.",
